{"about_the_game":"Cairn: Mathair\u2019s Curse is a heartfelt, Scottish turn-based story driven JRPG about a boy and his mother, in an adventure that explores love, loss and family. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302530/extras/sunset.gif?t=1733676718\" /><br>\u2800<br><strong>Featuring:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u25d8 Full-length single-player JRPG</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u25d8 A story-rich narrative steeped in Celtic mythology and Scottish culture</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u25d8 Use your dreams to enter a mysterious dark realm</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u25d8 Funky turned-based combat with cultists, Haggis and stop-signs!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u25d8 Solve puzzles to unlock areas, find presents and more!</ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302530/extras/montage.gif?t=1733676718\" /><br><br>Explore hand-crafted locations, from quaint seaside villages to ancient underground caverns and secret high-tech lairs. The world of Cairn: Mathair's Curse is inspired by life in the Scottish Highlands in the early 2000s. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302530/extras/dresser.gif?t=1733676718\" /><br><br>Fight unusual and wacky enemies, including wild roaming haggis', bewildered stop signs and an odd group of cultists bent on destroying the world. Use character unique skills to tip the balance and unleash devastation on your foes and combine the skills of your friends to tactically defeat your enemies. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302530/extras/band.gif?t=1733676718\" /><br><br>A soundtrack hand-crafted for the world of Cairn: Mathair's Curse - from bouncing combat music to spooky exploration ambience and heart-breaking melodies.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite